            "title": "華盛頓郵報稱特朗普今夏拒批4億美元對台灣的軍援計劃",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"華盛頓郵報稱特朗普今夏拒批4億美元對台灣的軍援計劃\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pRyxQiHp1C2vtbwIvXfF7g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/69c8ffb0-9509-11f0-a62d-de1f2301969c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">華盛頓郵報稱特朗普今夏拒批4億美元對台灣的軍援計劃</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
