        {
            "title": "美國總統特朗普威脅吊銷對他批評過頭的電視台牌照",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 美國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>表示，如果美國廣播電視網絡對他批評過頭，應對其牌照進行審查，相當於對媒體自由發出最廣泛的威脅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「電視網絡那些晚間節目所做的就是攻擊特朗普，」特朗普周四在空軍一號上對記者說。「我覺得也許應該吊銷他們的牌照。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他為ABC決定無限期停播吉米·坎摩爾的節目進行辯護時發表了上述講話，這位深夜節目主持人此前就共和黨活動人士查理·柯克槍擊事件發表的言論引發強烈反應。幾天前特朗普還對紐約時報提起150億美元的誹謗訴訟。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9f17114f-9982-3165-b9a4-52ee7c747170-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美國總統特朗普表示，如果美國廣播電視網絡對他批評過度，應對其牌照進行審查。川普在空軍一號上接受記者採訪時還表示，「誰」都可以取代吉米·坎摩爾。資料來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JvS86BWy6AeEvKFqD8MTvA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fe1e60dbb876bb93919c95d1d2c43002\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美國總統特朗普表示，如果美國廣播電視網絡對他批評過度，應對其牌照進行審查。川普在空軍一號上接受記者採訪時還表示，「誰」都可以取代吉米·坎摩爾。資料來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普及其共和黨盟友長期以來就抱怨美國主流媒體對保守派存在偏見。特朗普曾多次呼籲CBS、ABC和NBC撤掉那些經常批評其政府的深夜喜劇節目主持人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普的言論打破了美國憲法所賦予的言論和新聞自由的悠久傳統。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國會共和黨人大多對這些問題保持沉默或支持川普。周四，幾位重量級共和黨議員表示，停播吉米·坎摩爾的節目是ABC的決定，而非聯邦通信委員會(FCC)的舉動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Threatens Licenses of TV Stations That Criticize Him (3)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Hadriana Lowenkron、Michelle Jamrisko、Ben Holland、Derek Wallbank、Romy Varghese.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E5%90%8A%E9%8A%B7%E5%B0%8D%E4%BB%96%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E9%81%8E%E9%A0%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%B0%E7%89%8C%E7%85%A7-003238910.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-19 09:20:43",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中資公司香港配股唯一買家 Infini高調吃進賺得盆滿缽滿",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 一家香港投資公司在飆升的市場中通過高調配股搶購中國股票，短期內就實現了大量獲利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由Tony Chin創立的多策略投資公司Infini Capital在認購軟件供應商微盟周三的定向增發後，一天內就錄得約2.3億港元（3000 萬美元）獲利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周早些時候，它對協鑫科技的投資三天內就斬獲近10億港元，因此間該股上漲了8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博匯總的數據顯示，Infini在過去三個月中至少完成了五筆此類交易，其目標主要是科技公司，包括商湯科技和第四範式。該基金以約4%至9%的折讓價買入這些股票。假設它繼續持有，配售產生的賬面利潤就超過了30億港元。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6042adcf-6ded-359e-a12d-02fb38bf1712-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/S_Jrq3BAjt5IAXpIi8VR6g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b1d415d0d1c761889f8cb3059a2a7bc1\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Infini的投資者關係團隊暫未回覆通過電子郵件發送的評論請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國股票的火爆行情推動了配股後的強勁回報。人工智能開發商商湯科技的股價今年已飆升76%，而第四範式則上漲了26%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/S0U5dSu27f0bHxa6knevsw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8352347295dd27d917af87a229f96233\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Infini Emerges as Sole Buyer in String of China Share Placements</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%85%8D%E8%82%A1%E5%94%AF-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6-infini%E9%AB%98%E8%AA%BF%E5%90%83%E9%80%B2%E8%B3%BA%E5%BE%97%E7%9B%86%E6%BB%BF%E7%BC%BD%E6%BB%BF-171612618.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-19 09:35:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
